    pol:hasText "each member state shall submit to the commission a report on the implementation of its national policy framework by 18 november 2019, and every three years thereafter. those reports shall cover the information listed in annex i and shall, where appropriate, include a relevant justification regarding the level of attainment of the national targets and objectives referred to in article 3(1)." ;
