    pol:hasText "by 18 november 2017, the commission shall submit to the european parliament and to the council a report on the assessment of the national policy frameworks and their coherence at union level, including an evaluation of the level of attainment of the national targets and objectives referred to in article 3(1)." ;
    pol:hasDate "2017-11-18"^^xsd:date .

