pol:EU_32014L0094_Title_0_Chapter_0_Section_0_Article_10_Provision_5 a pol:Provision ;
    pol:hasText "by 31 december 2020, the commission shall review the implementation of this directive, and, as appropriate, submit a proposal to amend it by laying down new common technical specifications for alternative fuels infrastructure within the scope of this directive." ;
